and say that So-eun called the police.

522
00:48:20,314 --> 00:48:22,024
Wait, where's Ha-na?

523
00:48:23,358 --> 00:48:24,276
What?

524
00:48:35,704 --> 00:48:39,041
You're one persistent bitch.
Is it because you survived that alone?

525
00:48:39,124 --> 00:48:41,084
Shut your mouth.

526
00:48:41,168 --> 00:48:43,003
Those guys probably have no idea

527
00:48:43,712 --> 00:48:45,339
how you survived that day.

528
00:48:46,381 --> 00:48:48,008
I said, shut your mouth!

529
00:48:53,055 --> 00:48:55,557
Go ask your mommy
for some more breast milk.

530
00:48:57,142 --> 00:48:58,185
Oh, she's dead, right?

531
00:49:04,358 --> 00:49:05,400
Shit.

532
00:49:05,942 --> 00:49:07,861
You persistent bitch.

533
00:49:13,325 --> 00:49:14,451
Damn it!

534
00:49:17,287 --> 00:49:19,331
JUNGJIN UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL

535
00:49:20,707 --> 00:49:21,792
All done.

536
00:49:21,875 --> 00:49:25,420
Does it mean those men will be punished?

537
00:49:25,504 --> 00:49:26,880
Yes, of course.

538
00:49:26,963 --> 00:49:29,007
Thanks to you,
who bravely told us everything.

539
00:49:29,091 --> 00:49:30,717
Thank you.

540
00:49:30,801 --> 00:49:32,594
Get some rest. I'll visit you again.

541
00:49:38,350 --> 00:49:41,353
My gosh. You're amazing, So-eun.

542
00:49:41,436 --> 00:49:43,021
Thanks, Mun.

543
00:49:43,105 --> 00:49:44,231
For what?

544
00:49:44,314 --> 00:49:47,651
I had a dream last night.

545
00:49:47,734 --> 00:49:51,530
In my dream, you beat up those bad guys

546
00:49:51,613 --> 00:49:54,116
and saved me. You were so cool.

547
00:50:03,625 --> 00:50:05,252
It makes me anxious even now.

548
00:50:06,545 --> 00:50:08,672
Had anything bad happened to her,
I would have…

549
00:50:10,465 --> 00:50:11,299
I'd…

550
00:50:12,634 --> 00:50:13,552
In the end,

551
00:50:14,845 --> 00:50:16,054
So-eun helped us catch…

552
00:50:17,180 --> 00:50:18,432
Cho Tae-sin.

553
00:50:24,062 --> 00:50:25,272
-Get lost!
-Take responsibility!

554
00:50:25,355 --> 00:50:26,815
-It's all on you!
-Be responsible!

555
00:50:26,898 --> 00:50:28,942
-Take down Taesin!
-This is our basic right!

556
00:50:32,237 --> 00:50:34,156
-He's coming out!
-A comment, please!

557
00:50:34,239 --> 00:50:36,658
-Say a few words.
-Do you admit to the charges?

558
00:50:36,742 --> 00:50:37,743
A comment, please!

559
00:50:37,826 --> 00:50:38,660
-Sir!
-Over here!

560
00:50:38,744 --> 00:50:40,704
Any comment as the chairman of Taesin?

561
00:50:40,787 --> 00:50:41,872
Apologize to the kids!

562
00:50:41,955 --> 00:50:45,083
This is a mere conspiracy
against me and Taesin Group.

563
00:50:45,751 --> 00:50:47,627
I'll cooperate with the investigation.

564
00:50:47,711 --> 00:50:48,962
-Sir!
-Is everything true?

565
00:50:49,045 --> 00:50:49,921
A comment, please!

566
00:50:50,005 --> 00:50:51,715
-Sir!
-Do you admit to the charges?

567
00:50:51,798 --> 00:50:53,425
-Look over here!
-Hey!

568
00:50:54,801 --> 00:50:56,011
-My gosh!
-What was that?

569
00:50:56,094 --> 00:50:56,928
What happened?

570
00:50:57,012 --> 00:50:58,555
-Let's get out of here.
-Everyone!

571
00:50:58,638 --> 00:51:01,349
-What's going on?
-Huge articles on the front page, please!

572
00:51:01,933 --> 00:51:05,729
That evil son of a bitch
doesn't even deserve to be called human.

573
00:51:06,480 --> 00:51:08,982
We can put up with all kinds of jerks,

574
00:51:09,524 --> 00:51:12,486
but not those who hurt our children!

575
00:51:13,320 --> 00:51:15,447
-Get down.
-I'm counting on you reporters!

576
00:51:17,282 --> 00:51:18,784
Our old man's trying hard.

577
00:51:22,913 --> 00:51:24,498
-Goodness.
-What the…

578
00:51:25,999 --> 00:51:27,250
Jeez! Enough!

579
00:51:28,001 --> 00:51:29,336
-Calm down.
-You piece of…

580
00:51:29,419 --> 00:51:30,921
-Out of the way!
-Move back!

581
00:51:35,634 --> 00:51:36,676
A comment, please!

582
00:51:36,760 --> 00:51:38,512
-How do you feel?
-A comment, please.

583
00:51:38,595 --> 00:51:43,099
They'll finally reassess
the entire ICT project.

584
00:51:43,642 --> 00:51:44,768
The kids…

585
00:51:46,061 --> 00:51:47,854
can finally drink clean water.

586
00:51:47,938 --> 00:51:49,648
-Sir!
-Do you admit to everything?

587
00:51:49,815 --> 00:51:51,149
-Look here!
-Say a few words!

588
00:51:51,233 --> 00:51:52,150
-Sir!
-Get lost!

589
00:51:52,859 --> 00:51:54,152
-Get lost!
-You bastard!

590
00:51:54,236 --> 00:51:56,321
-Let's go.
-Hold on!

591
00:51:56,404 --> 00:51:58,323
-Convict him!
-Take responsibility!

592
00:51:59,783 --> 00:52:01,618
That girl can't do anything alone,

593
00:52:01,701 --> 00:52:03,537
but if those rats show up together

594
00:52:03,620 --> 00:52:05,330
with their staffs, we'll be screwed.

595
00:52:05,997 --> 00:52:08,208
If you don't have a plan,
we should just leave.

596
00:52:09,209 --> 00:52:10,126
Come on!

597
00:52:10,210 --> 00:52:12,587
Jeez. Cho Tae-sin's been arrested,

598
00:52:12,671 --> 00:52:14,297
so we have no money. What now?

599
00:52:14,923 --> 00:52:16,758
We're almost there. Let's hang in there.

600
00:52:18,009 --> 00:52:19,678
When will we get there?

601
00:52:24,766 --> 00:52:25,642
Soon.

602
00:52:30,730 --> 00:52:33,108
Is Ha-na really okay?

603
00:52:33,650 --> 00:52:34,776
Is she hiding somewhere

604
00:52:34,860 --> 00:52:36,862
beating herself up
for losing Baek Hyang-hui?

605
00:52:37,612 --> 00:52:40,323
Even so, it's strange
that she hasn't contacted us.

606
00:52:40,407 --> 00:52:43,243
They say some people experience
teenage angst later on in life.

607
00:52:45,912 --> 00:52:47,455
-Hey!
-You guys are here.

608
00:52:47,539 --> 00:52:49,541
Hey, what happened? We were all worried.

609
00:52:49,624 --> 00:52:50,959
Where have you been?

610
00:52:51,042 --> 00:52:53,169
-I told you not to wander alone--
-I'm sorry.

611
00:52:53,253 --> 00:52:54,296
How's So-eun?

612
00:52:54,379 --> 00:52:56,464
Oh, she's back in the hospital,
safe and sound.

613
00:52:56,548 --> 00:52:57,883
And those jerks got arrested.

614
00:52:57,966 --> 00:52:58,800
Are you okay?

615
00:52:59,634 --> 00:53:01,094
Are you all right, Ha-na?

616
00:53:03,430 --> 00:53:05,181
I found Shin Myeong-hwi.

617
00:53:05,807 --> 00:53:06,725
Seriously?

618
00:53:06,808 --> 00:53:07,809
For real?

619
00:53:07,893 --> 00:53:09,102
Where is he now?

620
00:53:15,650 --> 00:53:16,735
Damn it!

621
00:53:31,499 --> 00:53:33,043
I'm asking you where he is!

622
00:53:33,627 --> 00:53:34,628
Sit down.

623
00:53:34,711 --> 00:53:37,631
Yes, calm down.
Let's listen to what Ha-na has to tell us.

624
00:53:41,468 --> 00:53:43,303
Baek Hyang-hui has become stronger.

625
00:53:44,012 --> 00:53:47,682
Even if we were to activate the barrier,
it may not be enough for both of them.

626
00:53:47,766 --> 00:53:50,018
They know what cards we're holding,

627
00:53:50,101 --> 00:53:52,604
but we have no way of gauging
what they can really do.

628
00:53:52,687 --> 00:53:54,189
Is there a way

629
00:53:54,773 --> 00:53:56,942
we can summon Shin when she's not around?

630
00:53:57,025 --> 00:53:59,444
That'd be nice,
but how do we separate her from him?

631
00:54:00,153 --> 00:54:02,989
One good thing is that
it seems like the barrier

632
00:54:03,073 --> 00:54:04,282
hurt Shin Myeong-hwi.

633
00:54:04,866 --> 00:54:07,494
That's why he's trying to recover
in hiding.

634
00:54:07,577 --> 00:54:09,704
If he's trying to recover in hiding…

635
00:54:09,788 --> 00:54:11,122
My gosh.

636
00:54:11,206 --> 00:54:13,208
More lives are being sacrificed.

637
00:54:13,291 --> 00:54:17,420
I bet Cho Tae-sin has been helping him.

638
00:54:17,504 --> 00:54:20,924
Now that Cho's out of the picture,
the only one who can help him is…

639
00:54:23,093 --> 00:54:24,302
Baek Hyang-hui.

640
00:54:26,429 --> 00:54:30,100
Why don't we wait until
that crazy wench steps out and attack him?

641
00:54:30,767 --> 00:54:31,726
Let's give it a shot.

642
00:54:31,810 --> 00:54:33,353
Then we can summon the spirit.

643
00:54:33,436 --> 00:54:35,230
The evil spirit inside Shin Myeong-hwi.

644
00:54:35,313 --> 00:54:37,649
If we do that,
we can free my parents' souls

645
00:54:38,400 --> 00:54:40,193
as well as all the other souls

646
00:54:41,695 --> 00:54:43,363
that are locked inside him now.

647
00:54:44,572 --> 00:54:46,116
We must do it as soon as we can,

648
00:54:46,199 --> 00:54:48,618
before Shin Myeong-hwi
becomes even stronger.

649
00:54:56,835 --> 00:54:59,838
I really shouldn't let him
boss me around like this.

650
00:55:02,048 --> 00:55:05,176
How many more lives must I kill
to outpower him?

651
00:55:21,276 --> 00:55:22,360
Let's pull this off.

652
00:55:22,444 --> 00:55:23,820
This may be our last chance.

653
00:55:23,903 --> 00:55:25,030
Stay calm and focused.

654
00:55:25,947 --> 00:55:28,658
-We've done this once, you know.
-All right, let's go.

655
00:57:04,129 --> 00:57:06,131
It's good to see you here.

656
00:57:06,214 --> 00:57:07,215
Don't be delusional.

657
00:57:07,882 --> 00:57:09,843
It's not like I wanted to see you!

658
00:57:13,847 --> 00:57:18,226
If I kill one of you,
this will go to shit, right?

659
00:57:19,769 --> 00:57:23,148
Then I should probably kill you.

660
00:57:31,364 --> 00:57:33,992
We're screwed. Those persistent little...

661
00:57:35,034 --> 00:57:36,286
<i>Who tailed you?</i>

662
00:57:36,369 --> 00:57:37,287
<i>They're here?</i>

663
00:57:37,954 --> 00:57:38,788
<i>All of them?</i>

664
00:57:38,872 --> 00:57:39,873
<i>No, not all of them.</i>

665
00:57:40,582 --> 00:57:43,460
<i>Someone followed you</i>
<i>and is eavesdropping on our conversation.</i>

666
00:57:43,543 --> 00:57:44,711
<i>What do we do now?</i>

667
00:57:44,794 --> 00:57:45,712
<i>Where can we go?</i>

668
00:57:46,212 --> 00:57:48,047
<i>If they barge in here with their staffs…</i>

669
00:57:48,131 --> 00:57:50,341
<i>We just need to kill one of them.</i>

670
00:57:53,011 --> 00:57:53,970
<i>I know who to target.</i>

671
00:57:55,889 --> 00:57:57,348
<i>That bitch will be an easy one.</i>

672
00:58:01,269 --> 00:58:02,145
Am I wrong?

673
00:58:03,438 --> 00:58:04,939
Should I kill everyone but you?

674
00:58:05,982 --> 00:58:07,859
Like what happened to your family.

675
00:58:11,112 --> 00:58:12,030
No, the barrier…

676
00:58:15,116 --> 00:58:15,992
No!

677
00:58:23,500 --> 00:58:25,752
-The barrier…
-It got deactivated.

678
00:58:30,507 --> 00:58:31,758
Is this fun for you?

679
00:58:31,841 --> 00:58:34,969
What's so fun about this? Answer me! Hey!

680
00:58:49,192 --> 00:58:50,610
Hey, by the way…

681
00:58:51,236 --> 00:58:52,987
Did you know?

682
00:58:53,613 --> 00:58:56,074
That your whole family would die?

683
00:58:59,869 --> 00:59:03,998
