all of them dead.

684
00:59:05,041 --> 00:59:06,709
Am I wrong?

685
00:59:16,094 --> 00:59:19,597
<i>He can't use his psychokinetic abilities</i>
<i>inside the barrier.</i>

686
00:59:21,724 --> 00:59:23,226
<i>What's going on?</i>

687
00:59:29,566 --> 00:59:33,403
Looks like your pathetic little prank
has ended.

688
00:59:35,113 --> 00:59:37,574
Then shall we begin the real fight now?

689
01:00:04,559 --> 01:00:05,977
What will you do now?

690
01:00:08,021 --> 01:00:09,522
I've become even stronger,

691
01:00:10,982 --> 01:00:12,859
and it's now time for you to give up.

692
01:00:18,823 --> 01:00:19,699
Says who?

693
01:00:27,582 --> 01:00:28,541
Says who?

694
01:00:31,252 --> 01:00:33,296
Who the hell says
it's time for me to give up?

695
01:01:27,159 --> 01:01:30,059
THE UNCANNY COUNTER

696
01:01:30,144 --> 01:01:32,271
We were both doomed to be alone
with no family.

697
01:01:32,355 --> 01:01:34,065
Do we have to finish each other off?

698
01:01:34,148 --> 01:01:35,441
Don't you dare compare me to you!

699
01:01:36,025 --> 01:01:38,069
We just have to get Shin Myeong-Hwi now.

700
01:01:38,152 --> 01:01:39,112
Please don't kill me.

701
01:01:39,195 --> 01:01:42,573
Let's kill them, one by one.

702
01:01:42,657 --> 01:01:43,783
What are you?

703
01:01:43,866 --> 01:01:44,701
A Counter?

704
01:01:44,784 --> 01:01:46,577
Wait, what? Coun... Who are you?

705
01:01:46,661 --> 01:01:48,329
You said we should bring this to an end.

706
01:01:48,413 --> 01:01:49,414
Is this the end?

707
01:01:49,497 --> 01:01:52,625
I'll be the one putting an end to it,
you bastard.

708
01:01:52,709 --> 01:01:54,419
Let's win today, no matter what.

709
01:01:54,502 --> 01:01:57,463
I pray that no one else dies.

